A vintage-style illustration of a workshop drafting table viewed from above, scattered with hand-drawn wireframe sketches on yellowed paper, pencils, a compass, and a ruler. In the center, one sketch shows a rough UI layout with boxes and lines representing buttons and navigation. A steaming coffee cup sits at the corner, and warm afternoon light streams across the wooden surface, casting soft shadows from the drafting tools. The color palette features sepia tones, muted blues, and warm amber hues, evoking a 1950s industrial design studio atmosphere.
